BodyText:
This email originated outside of TD SYNNEX.  Please help keep our organization and partners safe. It's up to us; think before you click.


I am not sure anyone can have much of an impact with this, I am just not showing stock in disty right now.

@InsightHPI@tdsynnex.com

Can you see when this sku is coming in - AN6B6UT#ABA?  TDS portal doesn't show an ETA date.




DAVID YBARRA  |  HP Business Development Manager - Acquisition |  Insight
c. 636.281.6160  |  insight.com

-----Original Message-----
From: Matthew Hofner <Matthew.Hofner@insight.com>
Sent: Wednesday, April 30, 2025 3:32 PM
To: David Ybarra <David.Ybarra@insight.com>
Subject: FW: Order #0337886416 - CAE USA, Inc - PO# DB-8000925

Hey David!

SO#: 0337886416

Can you help in "escalating" this to see if they can make/delivery quicker?

Client is in a bind.


MATTHEW HOFNER  |  Senior Account Executive, Preferred Accounts Group  |  Insight t. 630.848.4835  |  f. 310.630.5313  |  matthew.hofner@insight.com  |  insight.com

-----Original Message-----
From: Darlene Belka <Darlene.Belka@caemilusa.com>

To: Matthew Hofner <Matthew.Hofner@insight.com>

Hey there, sorry t be a pain...any word on this yet?  I have a pain, lol.

Thanks,
Darlene
